ning the electronic part of zT, but also showcases a\ncomputational framework for thermoelectric materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2020 13:08:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2020 01:51:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 19 Sep 2020 06:42:30 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2020 01:31:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-23"}
