 composed of common copper wires and tunable capacitors expand the range\nof NFC attacks to 49.6 centimeters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2020 04:50:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-23"}
